snippet.title: Thorns & Spells: Edge of Time (Open Beta Gameplay)
snippet.description:
Thorns & Spells is a free-to-play 2D MMORPG set in a persistent fantasy world, featuring real-time exploration and combat, class options, open PvP, & more!

The look/feel is like old school Ultima or Tibia, except with some newer age MMO elements.

www.thornsandspells.com

---------------
Highlights:

1:06 PvP
1:26 Death
1:42 Exploring a cave
3:23 Finding the witch trainer
5:12 Learning a new class (sorcerer)
